# Python Plugins

```bash
pip install xrpl-plugin
plugin-build path/to/plugin.py
# edit rippled.cfg to include the plugin.xrplugin in a [plugins] stanza
# run rippled with the `plugin` branch and submit plugin transactions to it
```
